# Meme Generator 🎨😂

This is a simple Meme Generator web application that allows users to view and generate random memes with a click.

## 🚀 Features

- 🎲 Random meme image generator
- 🔁 Get a new meme on button click
- 📱 Fully responsive for mobile and desktop
- 🌙 Light and dark mode (if added)

## 🛠 Built With

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript (Vanilla JS)

## 📸 Demo

👉 [Live Demo Link (if deployed)](https://your-live-demo-link.netlify.app)

## 🧠 How It Works

- Fetches random meme images from a public API
- Displays the image and updates on each button click

